;Notes<ref name="liner"/>
* "Don't Look Back" contains a portion of "[[Time of the Season]]" written by [[Rod Argent]].
* "Kaleidoscope Dream" contains a [[sampling (music)|sample]] from "I Got The" written and performed by [[Labi Siffre]].
* "How Many Drinks?" contains a sample from "[[We've Only Just Begun]]" written by [[Roger Nichols (songwriter)|Roger Nichols]] and [[Paul Williams (songwriter)|Paul Williams]], as performed by O'Donel Levy.

